Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:55.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:02:01.09,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Hope to be with you even after rebirth.....Rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:08.23,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今日が過去に変わる事で、明日が近づいて。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:15.48,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}そんな当たり前の事に　心は傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:19.56,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}あの日見た『世界』を　もう一度作ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:25.05,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}叶う時が　いつか来るなら　もう何もいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:32.84,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}まるで可能性が無いと　誰に揶揄されても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:37.70,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}次の君に逢える日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:41.65,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}繰り返し　巡る運命が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:45.01,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}たとえ　どんな道でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:48.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}決して　決して　諦めない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:52.41,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}『あした、またね。』　その『未来』を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:56.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}いつまでも失くさないように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:59.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}終わりのない始まり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:05.13,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今、君と夢見たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:09.88,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}繋いだ手を　離さないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:13.06,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:16.73,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Hope to be with you even after rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:18.94,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:08.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}用现在覆盖过去  未来就是这样步步走近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:15.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}如此理所当然  却依旧心殇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:19.56,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}那天你我所见的『世界』  再一次拼凑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:25.05,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}愿望实现之时若能到来  我再无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:32.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}即使被人嘲笑不切实际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:37.70,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}直到再见你为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:45.01,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}纵使颠沛轮回的命运再艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:48.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我也绝对  绝对  不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:52.41,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}『明天再见』  那一份『未来』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:56.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}让我们一直珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:59.75,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}一旦开始  再无休止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:05.13,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}现在我只愿和你一起  去瞭望梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:09.88,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}紧握的双手  不会再分离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:16.07,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心では何度も　好きと伝えた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.86,0:22:26.54,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想いは残るの？　わたし消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:36.55,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君の声　真っ直ぐな瞳　忘れない温もり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:45.28,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}記憶の中に閉じ込めたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:51.59,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}変えられないこと　変えてしまいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:23:01.84,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}何度でも運命の中を　笑いあって　ふざけあって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:07.62,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}「明日また会えるよね」　きっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:18.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}会いたい　ただひとつだけ願い叶うなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:16.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在心中曾千百次  向你表述过爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.86,0:22:26.54,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}是否会留下情思  即便我终会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:36.55,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你的声响  直视的目光  是无法忘怀的暖阳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:45.28,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想要烙刻在记忆上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:51.59,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}无从改变之物  却又想要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:23:01.84,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不断在轮回命运中  一同嬉笑  一同玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:07.62,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一定能够「明天再会」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:18.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}愿与你相会  若这唯一的祈愿将能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是啊  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能想起些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里的事情啊学校里的事情之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触碰盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触碰  盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盒子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说一股犯罪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.63,0:00:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了哦  进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸亏爱理还有多出来的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了这样的非常时刻而备着的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了暴走的时候而准备的么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:00:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh it suits you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.38,0:01:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盯着看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  结同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.07,0:01:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  我们很久以前开始就一直在研究这个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.34,0:01:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你热点牛奶  好让你好好睡一觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触碰  盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:25.86,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(603,302)}『剩下的时间』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后我重复了多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结  要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  现在什么都别问…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等等  结
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  脚上的伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不碍事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得找人来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织同学  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是想回避事故  结局就会变得越悲惨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像是在警告我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏…秋…秋山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就开始翘课吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想晒晒太阳就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像上了年纪的人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏  好想向你求助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就向你坦白一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛  哎  不过话说回来真的好想逃课啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那样是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长眠不起的人？是出租车司机来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了  咱们学校好像也有好几个人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川同学知道刚才说的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  听说过一些传言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「内滨综合症」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在内滨周边频繁发生的迷一样的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无预兆的  人们突然陷入长眠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样再也不会醒来  迷一样的病症
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁着骚动还没有扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊  居然要我们调查幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺有趣的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不有趣嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}「幽灵」？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}就是Ghost
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵的真身就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}总之明天先开始找人取证  然后再实地调查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}好麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我觉得…我待在这里就好？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:06:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准确的说是由于不断穿越回同一段时间而产生的我的残像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}是其他时间线上的我重合起来  受到量子振动的影响而产生的投影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不行的嘛  佳织也一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又引发了其他严重的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某个时间线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到啊  真伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么情况  影像？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的影子接触的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时间线的东八重子  据我所知再也没有醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测下来恐怕是因为量子振动的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有意识被拉入其他时间线去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说附近又出现了  「内滨综合症」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕啊  至少能知道发病原因也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是幽灵干的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}等…等等奏  别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「内滨综合症」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有以下三种情况  会让人容易受到量子振动的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接接触到我的影子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然波长一致的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是  对我想要改变未来这件事进行干涉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人发病的概率都会增加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就来决定一下幽灵调查小组的分组吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}去抓Japanese ghost吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是幽灵还是内滨综合症
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着我进行时间跳跃的次数增加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生的频率会越来越高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这里的成员中的某一个因此陷入沉睡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间就会丧失连续性  在未来我就不会被制作出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存在本身就会消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  佳织同学也就无法回避事故…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我是和谁一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让奏能带上笑容…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和秋山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就和佳织一组了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这里是报告目击到幽灵最多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他还有东西突然坠落  窗户玻璃振动之类的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来没什么东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我被传送回来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是还残留着量子振动的影响呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川害怕幽灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不怎么怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是呢  都这么大了居然还会怕幽灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你直接叫我名字了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不好意思  一不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来最开始相遇的时候你也是叫我奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}什么声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  闹得真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化节的准备也很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就剩委托给我们的幽灵调查了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支仓同学快来  柔道部和空手道部…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受了伤的话  佳织就可以躲过受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是在其他的时间线上验证过了的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起  结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  佐佐木同学没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这之后就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所抗衡的时间的修正  因果的锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的力量十分强大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会之后再说明理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请暂时在这里待一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结  哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是限制佳织自身的行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会引发完全无法预料的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对现实的的介入不得不谨慎进行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不以最小的介入对事故进行回避的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是可以的  什么又是不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断地重复  得出了答案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  这次肯定可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不那么痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么幽灵事件也就告一段落了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}真是的  柔道部也是  电影研究学会也是  都不干点正事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese ghost  明明好想见一面的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断增多的我的影子  内滨症候群
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我进行时间逆行这件事本身都会受到阻挠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前  不救出佳织同学的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也为了奏的笑容…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了古川  还在疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我救下佳织同学  未来就会因此改变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  我的存在本身又…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我就是为了这个才在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对结怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  你问怎么看…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}这个Symptom的意思是前兆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}Boldness是勇敢的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}真爱来临的前兆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}对男性来说就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然问我这个我也答不上来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢结吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和古川也才刚认识不久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你为什么要问这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  只是问问而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那个时候我没能明确地否定自己喜欢古川
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底…是怎么想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织请假了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像身体不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不舒服？  怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在为止都没发生过这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找佳织有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因呢！？  你有什么线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这也不能算是原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  古川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相机怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！？  奏！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川  你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去佳织同学家里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天佳织同学不可能请假的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是有什么理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织同学请假的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织不来难道会有什么麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我们都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文学会的一员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天一定会把佳织带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止我一个人  大家也都很担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我顺路买些什么东西带回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  那就  布丁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了  告诉大家明天我会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思让大家为我担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结  脚没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你又和奏吵架了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起用这个相机拍张照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  突然之间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正好也想试试传统相机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那机会难得  干脆就在外面拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这才是天文学会的感觉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:15:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那下拍好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样的时间能一直延续下去就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话想和你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支仓同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳…  不  佐佐木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我佳织就好了  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才想对我说什么来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  其实呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  真是的  有凪沙学姐在真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是小小的玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是天文学会成员的徽章
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然迟了点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么开心事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为身为古川迷的我感受到你浑身上下散发出的欢快的气氛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花梨  来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生的事大都不会变化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我以为只不过是和以前一样的  时间的延长而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  结  曲奇烤好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支仓同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把烤好的曲奇送给那两个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…结
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结  你对奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能听到你的心里话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  对秋山同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前问过奏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问他对结怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然奏没有明确回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我认为他应该是喜欢结的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…也很喜欢奏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从以前就一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾经有一次想要放弃过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我无法对自己撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟我还是喜欢着奏的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  忽然说这种话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  要是那样我到底又是为什么才来到这里的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  结
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和佳织之间发生了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回应她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回应佳织同学的感情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是你最…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢谁是我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是喜欢佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是爱理  凪沙学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结  你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我马上就会消失不见的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失不见是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要转学去其他地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我说清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在无法说明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我能停留在这里的时间只剩下一点点了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定要对佳织…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将无法得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听不懂啊
